{"embedding_dim": 768, "data": [{"__id__": "rel-b8cd4014a33142d7c1d5f4b41d5173a0", "__created_at__": 1749578424, "src_id": "Kokki Kumar", "tgt_id": "Kumar's Father", "content": "Kokki Kumar\tKumar's Father\nfamily conflict,revenge\nKumar seeks revenge against his father for murdering his mother.<SEP>Kumar's father murders his mother and attempts to kill Kumar, driving Kumar's actions throughout the story.", "source_id": "chunk-6de205f59c9f8b9c3de2ec99bab27356", "file_path": "unknown_source"}, {"__id__": "rel-3c1882c2ff8e6a4088fd9a3d7bf2ac36", "__created_at__": 1749578424, "src_id": "Anbu", "tgt_id": "Kokki Kumar", "content": "Anbu\tKokki Kumar\nbetrayal,mentor-mentee,power struggle,succession\nAnbu initially mentors Kumar and provides him with opportunities within the gang, but their relationship deteriorates.<SEP>Kumar works for Anbu, eventually killing him to take over his business.", "source_id": "chunk-6de205f59c9f8b9c3de2ec99bab27356", "file_path": "unknown_source"}, {"__id__": "rel-7ba2b0dd9e75ef87f3149e4575a31e9a", "__created_at__": 1749578424, "src_id": "Kokki Kumar", "tgt_id": "Thamizhselvan", "content": "Kokki Kumar\tThamizhselvan\ncrime,employer-employee,political ambition,politics\nKumar works for Thamizhselvan, gaining political power through his criminal activities.<SEP>Thamizhselvan employs Kumar and gives him political power, but their relationship is transactional and ultimately strained.", "source_id": "chunk-6de205f59c9f8b9c3de2ec99bab27356", "file_path": "unknown_source"}, {"__id__": "rel-c0ccbe6b4198e4b71545972724648901", "__created_at__": 1749578424, "src_id": "Kokki Kumar", "tgt_id": "Murthy", "content": "Kokki Kumar\tMurthy\ngang warfare,political rivalry,rivalry\nKumar and Murthy are rivals, engaged in a violent conflict.<SEP>Murthy is Kumar's main rival, and their conflict leads to violence and death.", "source_id": "chunk-6de205f59c9f8b9c3de2ec99bab27356", "file_path": "unknown_source"}, {"__id__": "rel-c91dc9dbb8479dc5732cb32b840024a2", "