cal context of the gang violence.", "source_id": "chunk-6de205f59c9f8b9c3de2ec99bab27356", "file_path": "unknown_source"}, {"__id__": "rel-47697a91fcb48fb6d9cd6df36e8bd60e", "__created_at__": 1749578424, "src_id": "Opposition Party", "tgt_id": "Thamizhselvan", "content": "Opposition Party\tThamizhselvan\ncrime,politics,power\nThamizhselvan is a leader in the opposition party, showing the political landscape of the story.", "source_id": "chunk-6de205f59c9f8b9c3de2ec99bab27356", "file_path": "unknown_source"}], "matrix": ""}